    "description": "<strong>Pyre</strong> Pyre 是一款组队作战的 RPG 游戏。在游戏中，你将带领放逐者小队探索神秘的荒野大地，接受远古竞赛的试炼，寻找自由之路。谁将荣耀加身，谁将被永世放逐？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >由《堡垒》和《晶体管》创作团队精心打造的全新游戏世界：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/64e4359aa1e3587b4fbb032bb81b1dc8.poster.avif?t=1729114062\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/64e4359aa1e3587b4fbb032bb81b1dc8.webm?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/64e4359aa1e3587b4fbb032bb81b1dc8.mp4?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Supergiant</strong> 有史以来最大制作、最富魔幻色彩的游戏，不容错过！在探索称为“下界”的神秘大地时，结识形形色色想要重获自由的角色。<br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动作感十足的三对三战斗机制</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/9b8286a7978a97ca3a981aa9ac2eac69.poster.avif?t=1729114062\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/9b8286a7978a97ca3a981aa9ac2eac69.webm?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/9b8286a7978a97ca3a981aa9ac2eac69.mp4?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在紧张刺激的对战中打败各种敌人，每次胜利（或失败！）都会提高放逐者小队的悟性。每次仪式都要从你的小队中挑选三名成员，为他们装备神秘的护符和强大的技能。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的分支剧情，没有结局的游戏体验</h2>在 <strong>Pyre</strong> 中，你绝对不会丢失进度。无论是胜利还是失败，你的冒险都会继续。<strong>Supergiant</strong> 倾力打造贯串整个游戏剧情的交互式体验，每位玩家都会在其中获得独一无二的体验。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在对战模式中挑战好友</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/b84fd65ec37a4adbbdfb13a09a94271d.poster.avif?t=1729114062\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/b84fd65ec37a4adbbdfb13a09a94271d.webm?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/b84fd65ec37a4adbbdfb13a09a94271d.mp4?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>除单人战役模式以外，<strong>Pyre</strong> 还有一个双人直接对战模式，可以使你通过游戏的快节奏、充满仪式感的战斗挑战自己的好友。多达 20 名风格迥异的角色，可以使你从容组建三人小队。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >华丽、宏大的游戏画面</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/34a7d4fea2b323bb411eeea093ca382d.poster.avif?t=1729114062\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/34a7d4fea2b323bb411eeea093ca382d.webm?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/462770/extras/34a7d4fea2b323bb411eeea093ca382d.mp4?t=1729114062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Pyre</strong> 再次展示了《堡垒》和《晶体管》创作团队的出众才华。从生动的手绘插画到引起共鸣的原创音轨，Pyre 的每个元素都会使你沉浸在这个奇幻世界中。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >容易上手且支持自定义的游戏操控</h2>兼容游戏手柄和鼠标键盘，所有控件都为电脑量身定制。该游戏在战役和对战模式中提供各种难度的挑战。</li></ul>",
